data.description: Welcome home to this possible 4 bedroom ranch in northern Hillsdale County. Conveniently located between Litchfield and Jonesville for an easy commute to either area or to Jackson. Just shy of 2.5 acres makes a nice setup for a mini homestead. 2 full baths, full basement that could be finished for even more space to enjoy. Spacious living room with fireplace and large kitchen with center island. New hardwood floors, fresh paint, new water softener. Septic pumped last year. All appliances included.  Outdoor wood burner with LP backup for heat. Move in ready!
